[[File:Market_place_256.png|right]]
The '''Marketplace''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It allows transport of resources between cities and enables trade with other players by land. Also increases the tax income of connected buildings.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 5

